test case 1
Title: Check title "Welcome to GitHub!
Let’s begin the adventure" in the signup page

1. go to https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home
2. pay attention to the animated text

ER: the text ""Welcome to GitHub!
Let’s begin the adventure"" is displayed as a printable animation



test case 2
Title: Signup to GitHub with empty data

1. go to https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home
2. click "Continue" button

ER: User stay on the same page


test case 3
Title: Signup to GitHub with not valid email

1. go to https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home
2. fill in the field "enter your email" with data "fdsfsfsfsf"
3. click "Continue" button

ER: "Email is invalid or already taken" massage was displayed. User stay on the same page


test case 4
Title: Signup to GitHub with valid email and empty password

1. go to https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home
2. fill in the field "enter your email" with data "jilax33393@alvisani.com"
3. click "Continue" button
4. click "Continue" button or Enter


ER: User stay on the same page

test case 5
Title: Signup to GitHub with valid email and password with one character 

1. go to https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home
2. fill in the field "enter your email" with data "jilax33393@alvisani.com"
3. click "Continue" button
4. fill in the field "Create a password" with data "1" or another symbol
5. click "Continue" button or Enter


ER: "Password is too short
	Make sure it's at least 15 characters OR at least 8 characters including a number and a lowercase letter." massage was displayed. User stay on the same page



